The calculating mom is willing to buy four tickets to a concert and then given two to her son and two to the chosen vixen.

‘He'll go to the show with one of his buddies (no way he'll take a girl, he's to (sic) shy to ask them out) and you and your friend will be in the seats next to them,’ she writes.

Then the chosen girl will ‘spring into action’, start talking to her boy during the concert and will ‘eventually pick him up.’

The conniving mom has a very clear idea of how this first date should end. 

‘Ask him to take you somewhere after and ditch your friends. Then you seduce him and take his virginity,’ she writes.

