And it doesn’t end there, the future monster-in-law anticipates the fake relationship lasting beyond one night.

She write that she wants the chosen girl to keep dating him and ‘showing him different sex positions’ until he goes to college.

At that stage the scheming mom wants the women to gently let her boy go ‘so he'll have the confidence to date other girls once he's there.’

What a proposal, and in return the mom promises she’ll make the chosen girl’s ‘financial issues disappear’ and suggests the lucky girl may even get the car of her choice.

‘Please put your favorite type of car in the subject, to show that you're real,’ she writes.

